WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.620
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.740 --> 00:00:47.140
=Episode 1=

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:55.390
(Am I in a dream)

00:00:55.750 --> 00:00:56.670
(or the real world?)

00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:59.110
(Everything feels both real and unreal.)

00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:03.030
(Father, Mother.)

00:01:03.030 --> 00:01:04.000
(Where are you?)

00:01:09.870 --> 00:01:11.790
Father! Mother!

00:01:32.920 --> 00:01:35.560
Father... Mother...

00:01:38.860 --> 00:01:42.900
(Jiang Mansion)

00:01:50.230 --> 00:01:53.230
(I'm Jiang Ruoli,
the Chancellor's daughter.)

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:55.900
(I often foresee the future
in my dreams.)

00:01:55.900 --> 00:01:56.740
(Jiang Ruoli)

00:01:56.740 --> 00:01:59.210
In my dream, my parents

00:01:59.221 --> 00:02:00.760
were killed in the street on the night

00:02:00.760 --> 00:02:02.000
of the Lantern Festival.

00:02:02.710 --> 00:02:04.560
(Report)
Do it at the You hour.

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:08.430
(I mustn't let what happened
in the dream occur.)

00:02:38.240 --> 00:02:39.180
Another one.

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:40.640
Another one.

00:02:44.020 --> 00:02:46.180
(Jiang Huaikang, Supervisor;
Jiang Wanyue)

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:49.960
Uncle.

00:02:50.630 --> 00:02:52.520
You really kept us waiting.

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:54.150
Why are you so late?

00:02:54.750 --> 00:02:55.840
Where are your parents?

00:02:58.420 --> 00:03:00.500
(You hour)

00:03:00.760 --> 00:03:01.640
Come.

00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:02.510
Master.

00:03:02.520 --> 00:03:03.390
Master.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:04.520
Urgent news from the border.

00:03:04.520 --> 00:03:06.260
(Jiang Huai'an, Chancellor)

00:03:06.740 --> 00:03:07.973
(Grain carts are rolling north)

00:03:10.280 --> 00:03:11.120
I'll go take a look.

00:03:11.560 --> 00:03:12.400
Sure.

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:14.240
Mother,

00:03:15.520 --> 00:03:17.750
it must be something important.

00:03:18.470 --> 00:03:19.910
Stay at home with Father.

00:03:20.030 --> 00:03:21.870
I'll watch the lanterns
with Uncle's family.

00:03:22.430 --> 00:03:24.756
(Shen Shuanghua, Chancellor's wife)
Take care on the road.

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:26.360
Don't worry, Mother.

00:03:29.030 --> 00:03:30.190
Just before leaving,

00:03:30.190 --> 00:03:31.280
Mother suddenly felt unwell.

00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:32.726
She took some medicine;

00:03:33.190 --> 00:03:35.310
Father is currently in the carriage
looking after her.

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.360
Please forgive us, Uncle.

00:03:40.910 --> 00:03:41.910
In that case,

00:03:42.470 --> 00:03:44.680
watch the lanterns with us first.

00:03:45.630 --> 00:03:46.470
Ruoli, please.

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:09.240
Make way!

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:10.200
Move aside!

00:04:13.870 --> 00:04:15.150
Anyone in the way will be killed!

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:17.200
Go.

00:04:18.830 --> 00:04:21.190
(The men in black
from my dream really came.)

00:04:46.270 --> 00:04:47.110
Chase!

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:03.870
(Ruoli.)

00:05:50.310 --> 00:05:51.150
Over there!

00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:52.520
Catch her!

00:06:10.430 --> 00:06:12.000
(The man from my dream.)

00:07:10.830 --> 00:07:11.836
Thank you for saving me.

00:07:12.510 --> 00:07:13.600
You recognize me?

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:15.870
This is our first meeting.

00:07:16.310 --> 00:07:17.830
I'm Jiang Ruoli.

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:19.630
May I ask for your name?

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:21.480
My family will surely reward you.

00:07:22.630 --> 00:07:23.630
I'm Huo Linchuan

00:07:23.630 --> 00:07:24.720
(Huo Linchuan, Commander)

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:25.646
from the Duke's family.

00:07:25.950 --> 00:07:28.000
(The heir of the Duke.)

00:07:28.430 --> 00:07:29.480
Thank you.

00:07:39.740 --> 00:07:41.140
(Wuyou Ferry)

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:43.120
(Should I tell him?)

00:07:44.480 --> 00:07:45.510
You keep staring at me.

00:07:46.830 --> 00:07:48.223
Is there something you want to say?

00:07:50.310 --> 00:07:51.630
I want to tell you

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:53.300
to never go to Wuyou Ferry.

00:07:56.870 --> 00:07:58.190
How do you know

00:07:58.720 --> 00:08:00.040
my next destination?

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:02.920
I...

00:08:11.270 --> 00:08:13.680
If you insist on going,

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:15.270
once you hear the crows caw,

00:08:15.270 --> 00:08:16.240
be careful of both sides.

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.186
There will be an ambush.

00:08:45.150 --> 00:08:46.240
(I'm sorry, Mr. Huo.)

00:08:46.910 --> 00:08:49.960
(Father, Mother, wait for me.)

00:08:52.700 --> 00:08:55.420
(Wuyou Ferry)

00:09:23.270 --> 00:09:25.150
Huo Linchuan.

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:27.600
Who exactly are you?

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:38.720
If you insist on going,

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:40.670
once you hear the crows caw,

00:09:40.960 --> 00:09:41.960
be careful of both sides.

00:09:42.390 --> 00:09:43.336
There will be an ambush.

00:10:13.630 --> 00:10:14.960
(Just as she said.)

00:10:16.150 --> 00:10:18.670
(I should visit her
to find out the truth.)

00:10:19.900 --> 00:10:23.100
(Jiang Mansion)

00:10:26.740 --> 00:10:28.940
(Jiang Mansion)

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:13.080
Ruyan.

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:14.440
Ruyan.

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:17.200
Tao.

00:11:18.790 --> 00:11:19.910
Tao.

00:11:25.670 --> 00:11:26.510
Mother!

00:11:31.390 --> 00:11:32.230
Mother...

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:35.320
Father...

00:11:37.390 --> 00:11:40.630
Why did I fail to change
the ending of the dream?

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:41.680
Why?

00:11:42.870 --> 00:11:43.750
Why?

00:11:59.270 --> 00:12:00.480
It was you.

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:44.390
Not me.

00:13:03.670 --> 00:13:04.720
I'm sorry

00:13:05.320 --> 00:13:07.320
for failing to protect you.

00:13:37.550 --> 00:13:39.150
Ten lifetimes of reincarnation.

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:41.510
Only one life remains.

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:47.630
This is the last chance.

00:14:09.260 --> 00:14:10.780
♪The dream shattered♪

00:14:11.140 --> 00:14:12.820
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:14:12.820 --> 00:14:14.460
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:14:15.340 --> 00:14:16.900
♪How vague♪

00:14:17.300 --> 00:14:18.820
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:14:18.820 --> 00:14:21.060
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:14:21.860 --> 00:14:24.460
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:14:24.940 --> 00:14:27.780
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:14:28.420 --> 00:14:33.180
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:14:33.780 --> 00:14:35.300
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:14:35.700 --> 00:14:39.260
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:14:39.980 --> 00:14:41.540
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:14:41.940 --> 00:14:45.660
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:14:46.380 --> 00:14:49.220
♪Life after life♪

00:14:49.700 --> 00:14:52.380
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:14:53.020 --> 00:14:57.100
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:14:57.180 --> 00:15:00.220
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:15:00.380 --> 00:15:01.780
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:15:01.780 --> 00:15:04.900
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:15:04.980 --> 00:15:06.420
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:15:06.540 --> 00:15:10.300
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:15:11.020 --> 00:15:13.820
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:15:14.100 --> 00:15:16.940
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:15:17.260 --> 00:15:21.660
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:15:21.900 --> 00:15:24.820
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:15:24.940 --> 00:15:29.380
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:15:29.580 --> 00:15:35.300
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:15:35.740 --> 00:15:38.460
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:15:38.700 --> 00:15:41.420
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:15:41.860 --> 00:15:47.860
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪